eir own daring stunt.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTk3MDkxMDAyN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwODY5NzQyOQ@@._V1_SX214_.jpg','2013-03-15',5.9),(58,'Jack Reacher',2012,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0790724','tt0790724',NULL,1,'In an innocent heartland city, five are shot dead by an expert sniper. The police quickly identify and arrest the culprit, and build a slam-dunk case. But instead of confessing, the accused man writes the words, \"Get Jack Reacher.\" Reacher himself sees the news report and turns up in the city. The defense is immensely relieved, but Reacher has come to bury the guy. Shocked at the accused\'s request, Reacher sets out to confirm for himself the absolute certainty of the man\'s guilt, but comes up with more than he bargained for. Written by Anonymous','A homicide investigator digs deeper into a case involving a trained military sniper who shot five random victims.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTM1NjUxMDI3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjg1ODM3OA@@._V1_SY317_CR3,0,214,317_.jpg','2012-12-28',7.0),(59,'Identity Thief',2013,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2024432','tt2024432',NULL,1,'Sandy Patterson (Jason Bateman) gets a nice call confirming his name and other identifying information. The next thing he knows, a spa in Florida is reminding him of his appointment, and his credit cards are maxed out. With his identity stolen, Sandy leaves his wife, kids and job to literally bring the thief to justice in Colorado. But keeping tabs on the other Sandy (Melissa McCarthy) and run-ins with bounty hunters, is harder than he was expecting, and ultimately the cross-country trip is going to find both Sandys learning life tips from one another. Written by napierslogs','Mild-mannered businessman Sandy Patterson travels from Denver to Miami to confront the deceptively harmless-looking woman who has been living it up after stealing Sandy\'s identity.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3NzM5MTk2Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDQ4MjQ3OA@@._V1_SX214_.jpg','2013-02-08',5.6),(60