r own survival is more important than they could ever have imagined. Written by Overture Films','A pair of crew members aboard a spaceship wake up with no knowledge of their mission or their identities.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BNDQxNjc5NTMxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjg2NDE4Mg@@._V1_SX214_.jpg','2009-10-01',6.7),(547,'The Exorcist',1973,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0070047','tt0070047',NULL,1,'A visiting actress in Washington, D.C., notices dramatic and dangerous changes in the behavior and physical make-up of her 12-year-old daughter. Meanwhile, a young priest at nearby Georgetown University begins to doubt his faith while dealing with his mother\'s terminal sickness. And, book-ending the story, a frail, elderly priest recognizes the necessity for a show-down with an old demonic enemy. Written by Andrew Harmon <aharmon@erols.com>','When a teenage girl is possessed by a mysterious entity, her mother seeks the help of two priests to save her daughter.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BNzYwMDA0NTA3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDcwNDY3Mg@@._V1_SY317_CR0,0,214,317_.jpg','1973-12-26',8.0),(548,'Trance',2013,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1924429','tt1924429',NULL,1,'A fine art auctioneer mixed up with a gang joins forces with a hypnotherapist to recover a lost painting. As boundaries between desire, reality and hypnotic suggestion begin to blur the stakes rise faster than anyone could have anticipated. Written by Fox Searchlight','An art auctioneer who has become mixed up with a group of criminals partners with a hypnotherapist in order to recover a lost painting.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMjMzNjU1MTg5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTExMTcwOQ@@._V1_SX214_.jpg','2013-05-10',7.2),(549,'American Gangster',2007,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0765429','tt0765429',NULL,1,'Following the death of his employer and mentor, Bumpy Johnson, Frank Lucas establishes himself as the number one importer of heroin in the Harlem district of Manhattan. He does so by buying heroin directl